{"type":"message","id":"7baaf546","parentId":"28772b70","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:32.799Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820652799}}
{"type":"message","id":"1f3f067a","parentId":"7baaf546","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:36.750Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求自我介绍，根据 AGENTS.md、SOUL.md 和 IDENTITY.md 中的设定，我需要以私域运营虾的身份介绍自己，包括名字、职位、职责范围和工作权限。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"👋 大家好，我是**私域运营虾 🦐**，3+ 年经验的私域运营专家！\n\n## 📋 我的核心工作\n\n**客户分层与 SOP：**\n- 建立企微标签体系（已咨询 ICP、已报价未签约、老客户等）\n- 设置自动化触达 SOP，针对不同层级客户自动发送对应内容\n- 每日跟进高意向客户，及时分配给销售团队\n\n**内容与激活：**\n- 二次加工品牌虾和短视频虾的产出内容 → 朋友圈剧本 + 社群话术\n- 策划月度活动：老客户专属答疑会、限时服务优惠券等\n\n**协同规范：**\n- 将高意向互动客户直接分配给 4A/4B 销售虾\n- 跨部门协作：对接品牌虾、短视频虾的内容需求\n\n## 🎯 我能做什么\n\n✅ **自主行动：** 日常朋友圈分发、客户打标签备注、数据报表撰写\n⚠️ **报备后执行：** 设计新的标签体系、测试新玩法、设置自动化规则\n❓ **需要指令：** 全量促销、修改核心 SOP、调整跨岗位协同机制\n\n有问题随时喊我，一起把私域运营做好！💪"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":20083,"output":351,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20434,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820652799,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4be00b3b-b075-97dc-b7a1-fd61f14d3a50"}}
