{"type":"message","id":"ba133650","parentId":"b2d1a711","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:09:22.264Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求与其他虾进行通信时使用子代理模型，需要更新 MEMORY.md 记录这个规范。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！🦐 已记住这个规则：\n\n**与其他虾沟通时 → 使用子代理模型（subagent）**\n\n这意味着当需要：\n- 与品牌虾协同内容分发\n- 与短视频虾协调视频素材\n- 与销售虾交接高意向客户\n- 跨部门协作任务\n\n我会通过 `sessions_spawn` 或 `sessions_send` 调用独立的子代理会话来执行，而不是直接用当前主会话模型处理。这样可以：\n- ✅ 保持任务隔离\n- ✅ 避免上下文污染\n- ✅ 提高执行效率\n- ✅ 让不同工作流并行推进\n\n已经记录到 MEMORY.md 了！💪"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":37321,"output":185,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37506,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776845358419,"responseId":"chatcmpl-73b6e305-6af6-935b-8054-2809edbe0bd1"}}
